### Build, Test, Quality

- **Build system**: Gradle Java Library, group `com.github.mcaserta`
- **Java**: sourceCompatibility 17; modules configured via `module-info.java`

#### Common Commands
- `./gradlew build` — compile, test, package JARs (sources, javadoc)
- `./gradlew test` — run JUnit 5 tests
- `./gradlew clean` — clean build artifacts
- `./gradlew javadoc` — generate API docs
- `./gradlew jacocoTestReport` — coverage (XML enabled)
- `./gradlew publishToMavenLocal` — publish locally
- `./gradlew sonar` — SonarCloud analysis

#### Test Setup
- Framework: JUnit Jupiter 5.11.x
- Mocking: Mockito 5.18.0
- Extra provider for tests: Bouncy Castle `bcprov-jdk15on:1.70`
- Tests in `src/test/java` mirroring main packages; resources in `src/test/resources`

See [build.gradle](mdc:build.gradle).